      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable, budget-friendly ride that gets the job done? This vehicle is in fair condition \u2014 fully drivable and ready for your daily commute or weekend errands! You'll notice some visible wear on the exterior and interior, as expected for a car at this price point, but mechanically it's holding its own. A great opportunity for a practical buyer who wants dependable transportation without breaking the bank!",
