    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is being offered in poor condition, and I want to be completely upfront with any potential buyer about what to expect. The car does run and can be driven, but it has significant mechanical issues that will require attention. There is visible wear and damage both inside and out \u2014 expect rust, dents, and a worn interior. The engine runs but may exhibit rough idling, hesitation, or other performance concerns that should be addressed by a mechanic. This is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project vehicle, or needs basic transportation and is comfortable with the associated risks. No warranties or guarantees are implied \u2014 what you see is what you get, and I encourage any serious buyer to inspect the vehicle thoroughly before purchasing.",
      "price": 5500.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition, and the price reflects that reality honestly. The exterior shows considerable wear \u2014 expect multiple dents, scratches, paint peeling or heavily faded in several areas, and visible rust or corrosion on portions of the body. The interior is worn with torn or heavily stained upholstery, damaged trim pieces, and general signs of hard use over the years. Mechanically, this car has known issues and will likely require repairs or significant attention before it can be considered fully reliable \u2014 it is best suited for a buyer who is handy with vehicles, looking for a project car, or simply needs basic transportation on a tight budget. There are no warranties or guarantees implied, and we strongly encourage a thorough inspection before purchase. What you see is what you get \u2014 priced accordingly for an honest, straightforward transaction.",
